The photograph below shows <span class="short" aria-label="United States of America (USA)" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../usa" class="short" >US</a></span> President Barack Obama <sup><font color="#FF8800">1</font></sup> using
vIPer to make a secure telephone call. The photograph was published by
the manufacturer - <a href="../../../manuf/gd"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: General Dynamics">General Dynamics</span></a> &ndash;
on Twitter on  27 August 2013,
suggesting that the US President was one of its first users <a href="#ref_4">[4]</a>.
