             border=0
             />
            </div>
            </a>
            </td></tr><tr><td align=center>
          </td></tr></table>
<br />
<a href="img/viper_trudeau_1.jpg"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: Another photograph">Another photograph</span></a>, taken in the same office,
shows <a href="img/viper_trudeau_1.jpg"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: Trudeau in conversation with Mark ...">Trudeau in conversation with Mark Carney</span></a>
on 9 December 2019.
The vIPer is at the far side of the desk. Carney succeeded Trudeau
as prime minister on 14 March 2025.
It remains to be seen whether the Canadians will continue to trust American
security equipment, now that <span class="short" aria-label="United States of America (USA)" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../usa" class="short" >US</a></span> President Donald Trump wants to annex
Canada, and has forced other <span class="short" aria-label="United States of America (USA)" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../usa" class="short" >US</a></span> manu&#173;fac&#173;turers to takes measures against
foreign institutes that he dislikes.
